article_title: As Profits Roll In, Aetna To Expand On Obamacare Exchange In 2015

article_metadata.author: Bruce Japsen

og.description: Aetna said this morning it will expand its private health insurance products on government exchanges under the Affordable Care Act next year to the additional market of Georgia based on the company’s first-year successes. The Hartford-based health insurance giant, which raised its earnings guidance for the year to $6.45 to $6.60 [...]
